{"tid":154964,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"點同屋企人講想同朋友去旅行?","createTime":"2017-03-13T16:16:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-15T01:34:51.000Z","uid":57520,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"860cf1a092bc4791f9cffc9cb2e0a0277db89209","tid":154964,"uid":57520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T16:16:27.000Z","msg":"屋企人好嚴<br />\n未試過同朋友去旅行/去人屋企過夜<br />\n今日終於第一次開口問阿媽<br />\n好撚緊張<br />\n點知俾佢屌9我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講咗好耐，佢話<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你廿幾歲人喇我都管唔到啦你真係咁想去既你咪去囉</span></span><br />\n去個旅行姐洗唔洗搞到要發曬脾氣鬧我又不和咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴絲們平時係點同屋企人講想同朋友去旅行?"},{"pid":"9a82c76bbde4327062f4053abdd238acc63aa004","tid":154964,"uid":53798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T16:17:22.000Z","msg":"廿幾歲人<br />\n<br />\n去多幾次屋企人見你無事無變壞, 通常都唔會再管"},{"pid":"d0f727f21b522b949054c90bc87538e2b724aa4e","tid":154964,"uid":82602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T16:19:14.000Z","msg":"直接講 然後拋窒佢咩都買哂架啦 咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實咁大個唔會唔比你去嘅<br />\n又唔係問佢地攞錢去旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eacccf030fa69ec0bf8cdcbeb1b758d06956c60","tid":154964,"uid":56199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T16:19:19.000Z","msg":"你話「我諗住買埋你機票一齊去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」"},{"pid":"cbf4709cc6fbb105c5ac6bb008131efbde93a939","tid":154964,"uid":57520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T16:23:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>廿幾歲人<br />\n<br />\n去多幾次屋企人見你無事無變壞, 通常都唔會再管</blockquote><br />\n家中既皇太后表示唔撚高興<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌我身體弱仲去乜9"},{"pid":"f7a60dd988364d79c373b72cbe7dfdf3d0222353","tid":154964,"uid":57520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T16:24:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>直接講 然後拋窒佢咩都買哂架啦 咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實咁大個唔會唔比你去嘅<br />\n又唔係問佢地攞錢去旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咩都買曬會俾阿媽扔我落街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屋企唔受呢套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />會嚴懲"},{"pid":"7a10104d65d8461456a051065959d3b8352f6724","tid":154964,"uid":57520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T16:24:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你話「我諗住買埋你機票一齊去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」</blockquote><br />\n我去完今次都諗住過一個月同屋企人去旅行架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"982729a0267f3d7da55aa04bbd4a18a10f1f6a3e","tid":154964,"uid":72342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T16:24:45.000Z","msg":"睇黎你係永遠長不大既大細路"},{"pid":"a6dbb0591dcb322c93c056f7eb1d639b6a43ced4","tid":154964,"uid":78149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T16:24:52.000Z","msg":"等你老母死左先去"},{"pid":"d0d3a9ddde659dbeee7abbe434167c0467a2d88e","tid":154964,"uid":57520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T16:25:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇黎你係永遠長不大既大細路</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n毒撚之中既極品"},{"pid":"b33001258d75166534c847f80b88d959f9f306d2","tid":154964,"uid":57520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T16:26:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>等你老母死左先去</blockquote><br />\n唔好咒我老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1da941ac346fc88355b40af81093a1af182ee469","tid":154964,"uid":60831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T16:33:56.000Z","msg":"20幾歲仲要屋企人管 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\